"pid":"2e968dc20f225e61111efcc61435549763336d03","tid":361092,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T13:09:27.000Z","msg":"政府在1987年做的一個徹底的調查得出更清晰的數據：估計有33,000人在寨城居住。以城寨面積0.026平方公里推算，人口密度為每平方公里1,255,000人，屬於全世界人口密度最高的地方<br />\n<br />\n香港陸地總面積1106平方公里，如果全部按城寨密度推算，香港可以容納13.88億人口，即係岩岩好全中國既人口塞曬響香港"},{"pid":"12252d7de9e4d08f719b4588222aa6090f7d56d4","tid":361092,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T13:11:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢言下之意係要加支那人口比例<br />\n要殖民</blockquote><br />\n根本一直做緊<br />\n<br />\n下一步叫年輕人離香港去前海<br />\n或者去支那<br />\n<br />\n加快換血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1326266c28b1390817ea65c3c8e3179fd8e6e47a","tid":361092,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T13:13:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政府在1987年做的一個徹底的調查得出更清晰的數據：估計有33,000人在寨城居住。以城寨面積0.026平方公里推算，人口密度為每平方公里1,255,000人，屬於全世界人口密度最高的地方<br />\n<br />\n香港陸地總面積1106平方公里，如果全部按城寨密度推算，香港可以容納13.88億人口，即係岩岩好全中國既人口塞曬響香港</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會，至多12億左右<br />\n<br />\n減返有錢人冇影響唔洗住工廈"},{"pid":"f72246b4a5b7e009331128a3ce87216ef7c73ca0","tid":361092,"uid":62409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T13:39:31.000Z","msg":"每人住一格階磚夠啦"},{"pid":"206500694b090adc0db9acd5309cdd889098631e","tid":361092,"uid":130513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T15:27:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66b062b0bd6ea0db0f6cf46512ec18d7dc048372","tid":361092,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T15:29:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ce502e053967c9673bb29bb729ca22941f74aae","tid":361092,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T15:29:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0708f98596b8000cd1a71c7d3659a9337edb8b89","tid":361092,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T15:30:20.000Z","msg":"ON 9 9 ,  不如你問下有冇真香港人好鍾意成為 千萬人口城市 ?<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母狗官死全家啦"},{"pid":"2a9376f2d10517526ef743dd92de1889de092ba8","tid":361092,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T15:34:33.000Z","msg":"如果有一千萬高等教育人才, 應該亞洲屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce0ffa9012efea78922ade244f4180935043b3a","tid":361092,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T15:36:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果有一千萬高等教育人才, 應該亞洲屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你就想, 大部份低學歷支那移民"},{"pid":"bf3290dd4a2692f643ee349c059479a47935ea2c","tid":361092,"uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T16:32:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政府在1987年做的一個徹底的調查得出更清晰的數據：估計有33,000人在寨城居住。以城寨面積0.026平方公里推算，人口密度為每平方公里1,255,000人，屬於全世界人口密度最高的地方<br />\n<br />\n香港陸地總面積1106平方公里，如果全部按城寨密度推算，香港可以容納13.88億人口，即係岩岩好全中國既人口塞曬響香港</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n移平晒ｄ山　剷晒郊野公園<br />\n填平晒海　維港　水塘水庫<br />\n香港總面積係2,754平方公里<br />\n而且城寨舊啦　最高只係樓高12層<br />\n宜ｄ樓閒閒地都40層高　計佢36層　即3倍<br />\n<br />\n2,754 x 1,255,000 x 3 = 35億 x 3 = 105億<br />\n<br />\n地球人口問題搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3a/Kowloon_Walled_City.jpg/250px-Kowloon_Walled_City.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F3%2F3a%2FKowloon_Walled_City.jpg%2F250px-Kowloon_Walled_City.jpg&h=5d5ba8da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b767696a4a67773aa8c6b54c12f2b7723a3ff8de","tid":361092,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T16:32:46.000Z","msg":"填咗個水庫起新市鎮囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd335bced92af3706f8fc8ee44f559b9721c980","tid":361092,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2